  "category": "LEAD_INTELLIGENCE",
  "description": "leadIntelligence.modelMetadata.dataFreshnessDays is 14, indicating the ML scoring model was trained on data older than 7 days (the freshness threshold). Validator MUST emit an INTELLIGENCE_SCORES_STALE WARNING. The message is still valid.",
  "specRef": "LEX_CONFORMANCE §2 TC-014",
  "input": {
